OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781953372
OL,3,COne arrest during protests over Tommy
OL,4,CRobinson event
OL,6,FAround 200 protesters gathered in
OL,7,FOxford city centre to protest against
OL,8,Fan event featuring far-right activist
OL,9,FTommy Robinson.
OL,11,FThe Oxford Union debating society
OL,12,Fsparked controversy when it announced
OL,13,Fit would be hosting a debate entitled
OL,14,FThe West Is Right To Be Suspicious Of
OL,15,FIslam, featuring Robinson ` whose real
OL,16,Fname is Stephen Yaxley-Lennon `
OL,17,Falongside former actor Laurence Fox.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
