PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781953372
OL,3,COne arrest during protests over Tommy
OL,4,CRobinson event
OL,6,FProtesters took to New Inn Hall Street
OL,7,Fand Cornmarket Street on Wednesday
OL,8,Fnight, occupying either side of St
OL,9,FMichael Street where the event is
OL,10,Ftaking place.
OL,12,FChanting slogans such as "Oxford
OL,13,FUnion, shame, shame", they far
OL,14,Foutnumber the handful of counter-
OL,15,Fprotesters, carrying Union flags, who
OL,16,Fgathered on Cornmarket Street in
OL,17,Fsupport of Robinson.
OL,26,@tD@ZOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
