OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781953372
OL,3,COne arrest during protests over Tommy
OL,4,CRobinson event
OL,6,FThe two groups were separated by a
OL,7,Fpolice cordon, and numerous officers
OL,8,Fwere present across the area to
OL,9,Fmonitor the protest.
OL,11,FA minor incident took place on
OL,12,FCornmarket Street in which protesters
OL,13,Fbooed police officers, and a couple of
OL,14,Fdemonstrators appeared to throw water
OL,15,Fat them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
