FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781953372
OL,3,COne arrest during protests over Tommy
OL,4,CRobinson event
OL,6,FIn a statement, Thames Valley Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "The demonstrations passed off
OL,8,Fwithout significant incident, though a
OL,9,F20-year-old man from Kent was arrested
OL,10,Fon suspicion of assault by beating. He
OL,11,Fremains in custody.
OL,13,F"We would like to thank everyone who
OL,14,Fworked with our officers while we
OL,15,Ffacilitated peaceful protest."
OL,17,FOxford City Council closed St Michael
OL,18,FStreet to vehicles and pedestrians
OL,19,Fbetween 4pm and 11pm on Wednesday June
OL,20,F17 while the event was taking place.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
