FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781953372
OL,3,COne arrest during protests over Tommy
OL,4,CRobinson event
OL,6,FShops and some pubs in the area also
OL,7,Fclosed early because of the event and
OL,8,Fprotests.
OL,10,FThames Valley Police said: "We work
OL,11,Fclosely with a range of partners
OL,12,Fthrough well-established, safety
OL,13,Fadvisory structures to ensure events
OL,14,Ftake place safely and smoothly, while
OL,15,Fminimising disruption to our
OL,16,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@rD@\OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
