CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781953372
OL,3,COne arrest during protests over Tommy
OL,4,CRobinson event
OL,6,F"We support freedom of speech and are
OL,7,Fworking with the Oxford Union and
OL,8,Fother local stakeholders to facilitate
OL,9,Fthis event and any associated peaceful
OL,10,Fprotest."
OL,12,FParticipants in the debate who will
OL,13,Foppose Robinson include former Tory MP
OL,14,FJacob Rees-Mogg and activist Abdullah
OL,15,Fal Andalusi.
OL,17,FRees-Mogg released a YouTube video on
OL,18,FWednesday afternoon explaining why he
OL,19,Fbelieves the union is "right" to host
OL,20,FRobinson for a debate.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@IO]{D@WOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
