PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781953372
OL,3,COne arrest during protests over Tommy
OL,4,CRobinson event
OL,6,FHe said: "I think the best way to
OL,7,Fanswer him is to debate with him. You
OL,8,Fsee, if I just ignore him he won't go
OL,9,Faway, he won't lose his following and
OL,10,Fpeople will just say people like me
OL,11,Fare scared."
OL,13,FHe added that the Oxford Union would
OL,14,Fbe a "pointless society" without free
OL,15,Fspeech and that it "exists to argue".
OL,17,FIt was reported last month that the
OL,18,Fdebate had been delayed after
OL,19,Fsignificant outcry about Yaxley-
OL,20,FLennon's attendance.
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@LO]vD@FOUvD@XO]wD@TOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
