PN,38808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781953372
OL,3,COne arrest during protests over Tommy
OL,4,CRobinson event
OL,6,FThe most significant opposition came
OL,7,Ffrom faith leaders including the
OL,8,FBishop of Oxford, Steven Croft, and
OL,9,Ffounder of the Oxford Foundation, Imam
OL,10,FMonawar Hussain, who said they were
OL,11,F"disturbed and saddened" when he was
OL,12,Finvited to speak.
OL,14,FIan McKendrick, vice chairman of
OL,15,FOxford Stand Up To Racism, has
OL,16,Fpreviously accused Yaxley-Lennon of
OL,17,Finciting "violent race riots" in
OL,18,FSouthampton, Belfast and Glasgow over
OL,19,Fthe past weeks.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@XO]yD@JOUyD@]O]
